              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/904843-matt?shelf=philosophy">philosophy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/904843-matt?shelf=worst-of-the-worst">worst-of-the-worst</a>
          </div>
